The Major Issues Podcast celebrates the 20th anniversary of Infinite Crisis with a massive, all-in deep dive into the entire explosive road that led to DC’s universe-shattering event. From Identity Crisis and Countdown to Infinite Crisis to The OMAC Project, Day of Vengeance, Villains United, and the Rann–Thanagar War, the hosts break down every twist, betrayal, uprising, and cosmic wildfire that dragged the DC Universe to its absolute breaking point. It’s the ultimate, high-energy guided tour through the chaos, the shocks, and the long-burning fuse that made Infinite Crisis not just inevitable—but unforgettable.

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

